data.description: Check out this large 4 bedroom 2 1/2 bath split level with lots up upgrades. Newer roof, updated kitchen, updated bathrooms. Large flat lot for lots of entertaining possibilities. The sale also includes an additional .364 acre lot next to the home- tax id 24-000-08-0016-00-00000. Both lots total .824 of an acre!  Elementary school playground is within walking distance. Two car garage with lots of off street parking. Home boasts a large great room, a family room that is open to the dinning area and open kitchen with a large kitchen island for lots of cooking preparation. More pictures coming soon!
